out how you interact with this website (pages visited, time on site).\"]}]\na:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"4. How We Use Your Data\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"To deliver our Tech Due Diligence services as agreed in the engagement contract.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"To respond to inquiries and communicate about our services.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"To improve our website and service offerings.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"To comply with legal obligations.\"}]]}]]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"5. Legal Basis (GDPR)\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"We process your data based on:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Contract performance\"}],\" — processing necessary to deliver our assessment services.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Legitimate interest\"}],\" — responding to inquiries, improving our services.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Consent\"}],\" — where you have opted in to marketing communications.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Legal obligation\"}],\" — where required by applicable law.\"]}]]}]]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"6. Data Sharing\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with trusted service providers (cloud hosting, analytics) who process data on our behalf under appropriate data processing agreements. All assessment data is handled under strict NDA and is never shared with third parties.\"}]]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"7. Data Security\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Altimi is ISO 27001 certified. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data, including encryption in transit and at rest, access controls, and regular security assessments. All due diligence engagements are conducted through secure Virtual Data Rooms (VDRs).\"}]]}]\ne:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"8. Data Retention\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes described above. Contact data is retained for the duration of our business relationship plus 3 years. Assessment data is deleted or returned within 30 days of engagement completion, unless otherwise agreed.\"}]]}]\nf:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"9. Your Rights\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":\"Under GDPR / RODO, you have the right to:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Access your personal data\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Rectify inaccurate data\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Request erasure (“right to be forgotten”)\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Restrict processing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Data portability\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Object to processing\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Withdraw consent at any time\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4\",\"children\":[\"To exercise these rights, contact us at\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"mailto:wojciech.woziwodzki@altimi.com\",\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] underline underline-offset-4\",\"children\":\"wojciech.woziwodzki@altimi.com\"}],\".\"]}]]}]\n10:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"10. Cookies\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"This website uses only essential cookies required for functionality. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party advertising cookies. Analytics data is collected anonymously.\"}]]}]\n11:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"11. Changes to This Policy\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated “Last updated” date.\"}]]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] text-[24px] font-normal mb-4\",\"children\":\"12. Contact\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Altimi sp. z o.o.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"Wroclaw, Poland\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"mailto:wojciech.woziwodzki@altimi.com\",\"className\":\"text-[#0a1926] underline underline-offset-4\",\"children\":\"wojciech.woziwodzki@altimi.com\"}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"+48 509 299 889\"]}]]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-[#0a1926]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-[1540px] mx-auto px-[105px] max-md:px-6 py-16\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L6\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/logo-altimi-white.png\",\"alt\":\"Altimi\",\"width\":112,\"height\":28,\"className\":\"h-7 w-auto mb-6\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-white/60 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] mb-4\",\"children\":\"AI-powered system modernization for enginee